    "This innovative technique does not depend on parallel data, which is often scarce for low-resource languages, but instead learns translations between languages by sharing weights across different layers of the neural network.",
    "This approach demonstrates the potential of unsupervised learning techniques in reducing the data requirements and enhancing the scalability of machine translation systems.",
    "Human participants were involved in the data collection process for our study.",
    "Using a Google Form, they provided a few translations examples from Egyptian Arabic to Modern Standard Arabic.",
    "Following this, another individuals reviewed these translations for accuracy, making necessary corrections."
